title: Coronavirus: 77 more people die in State in worst daily toll
description: Total number of deaths from virus rises to 687, with 15,652 confirmed cases of infection
content:
The deaths of 77 patients - 32 males and 44 females - diagnosed with Covid-19 have been reported on Monday by the National Public Health Emergency Team (NPHET).
This is by far the highest daily total of deaths reported by the team.
